\begin_layout Enumerate
Ignoring the ends for the moment, for all the interior points we have 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{dT_{n}}{dt}=\frac{\kappa}{c\rho}\frac{T_{n+1}-2T_{n}+T_{n-1}}{\Delta x^{2}}$
\end_inset

